# T3 Chat Clone - Project Overview

## 🎯 Mission Statement
Win the T3 ChatCloneathon competition by building a superior multi-LLM chat application within the 3-day MVP timeline.

## 🏆 Competition Context
- **Competition**: T3 ChatCloneathon (cloneathon.t3.chat)
- **Deadline**: June 17, 2025 at 12:00 PM PDT
- **Prize Pool**: $10,000+ total ($5K first place)
- **Requirements**: Open source, GitHub hosted, permissive license
- **Judges**: Theo, Mark, Julius (vibes-based judging)

## 📋 Core Requirements (Must Have)
- Multi-LLM chat interface
- User authentication with sync
- Chat history persistence
- Modern, responsive UI

## 🎁 Bonus Features (Competitive Edge)
- Resumable streams
- Syntax highlighting
- File attachments (images/PDFs)
- Image generation
- Chat branching/sharing
- Web search integration

## 🎯 Success Criteria
1. **Functionality**: All core requirements working flawlessly
2. **Performance**: Instant navigation, fast streaming responses
3. **Design**: Beautiful, modern UI that impresses judges
4. **Innovation**: Unique features that stand out (resumable streams)
5. **Code Quality**: Clean, maintainable, well-documented code

## ⚡ Development Philosophy
- **Speed over perfection** during MVP phase
- **Quality over quantity** - polish core features
- **Mobile-first** responsive design
- **Real-time everything** - leverage Convex capabilities
- **TypeScript-first** for reliability and developer experience
